subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Brad Keselowski has a comfortable lead in the Sprint Cup standings, but most attention will be focused on Jeff Gordon and Clint Bowyer, who tangled last weekend.
